			<h2>About us</h2>
			<a href="http://www.isfit.org/">ISFiT</a>, the International Student Festival in Trondheim, is a non-profit organization made up of more than 400 student volunteers. The theme for ISFiT 2015 is corruption and the vision of ISFiT is to create a better future for young people in the world. This campaign is founded on this vision and we want to challenge people’s attitudes towards corruption. What are the solutions?
